# Files in THIS public repo that the publish-to-public.ps1 sync script must
# preserve when force-mirroring from KnudsenMorten/eldk-community-event-hub.
#
# Anything matching a pattern below survives the publish even though it does
# NOT exist in the private source. Use this for files that are deliberately
# public-only (issue templates with community-facing language, PR template
# without internal references, GitHub config that only makes sense in the
# public repo, etc.).
#
# Pattern syntax: PowerShell -like wildcards against the relative path from
# the public repo root, using forward slashes.

# Issue + PR templates -- worded for community contributors, distinct from
# the private repo's team-internal versions.
.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/*
.github/pull_request_template.md

# This file itself.
.publish-keep
